Spotify South Africa has revealed its most-streamed artists and tracks among local listeners. Drake has been the most popular artist on Spotify since its launch in South Africa last month, although local artists such as Jeremy Loops and Goldfish are also receiving attention. Popular music genres on Spotify South African include pop, hip hop, modern rock, indie, rock, and classic rock. According to Spotify, 15:00 on a Saturday is the most popular time for South Africans to listen to the music streaming service. Below are the most popular tracks and artists on Spotify South Africa for the last month.